Package: StatComp22083
Type: Package
Title: estimate probabilities based on 2PL IRT model
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-11-25
Author: Litian Xu
Maintainer: Litian Xu <xlt@mail.ustc.edu.cn>
Description: This package is created for computing item response probabilities and estimating parameters based on 2PL(discrimination and difficulty parameters) IRT model. Through MCMC method(using Gibbs update), we can obtain estimates of these two parameters and ability parameter of students.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp, stats,ltm, MASS, bootstrap, boot, microbenchmark, DAAG, scales, latex2exp, knitr, pander
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/xltskr/StatComp22083
BugReports: https://github.com/xltskr/StatComp22083/issues
